data.description: You do not want to miss this stunning two-story home, which is located in the Gildersleeve and Menchville School District! You will love the open floor plan, large kitchen with granite countertops, three and a half bathrooms, and a beautiful balcony, not to mention two primary ensuite bedrooms. Furthermore, this lovely home has soft water throughout the house and a water purification system in the kitchen. If you love to entertain, you will enjoy the spacious backyard, which is great for barbeques. It is also conveniently located near shopping centers, Fort Eustis, a dog park, and a community center. You must see this lovely house!
